---
// HowItWorks — 4 steps: Audit → Review Engine → Schema → Monitoring
---

<section class="hiw" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hiw__header reveal">
      <p class="section-tag" data-i18n="geo.hiw.tag">What We Do</p>
      <h2 class="hiw__headline" data-i18n-html="geo.hiw.h2">Four steps to make AI<br>recommend <span class="accent">your</span> business</h2>
      <p class="hiw__sub" data-i18n="geo.hiw.sub">We don't do SEO tricks. We engineer your business into the answer AI gives when customers ask "who's the best?"</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hiw__scroll">
    <div class="hiw__card reveal">
      <div class="hiw__card-video">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
          <source src="/assets/geo/what-we-do/audit-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw__card-body">
        <div class="hiw__step">STEP 01</div>
        <h3 class="hiw__card-title" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s1title">AI Visibility Audit</h3>
        <p class="hiw__card-text" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s1text">We scan ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, Claude, and 7+ AI platforms for your business. You get an instant score showing exactly where you stand — and where competitors beat you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw__card reveal">
      <div class="hiw__card-video">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
          <source src="/assets/geo/what-we-do/review-engine-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw__card-body">
        <div class="hiw__step">STEP 02</div>
        <h3 class="hiw__card-title" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s2title">Review Engine</h3>
        <p class="hiw__card-text" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s2text">We help your customers write reviews with the exact keywords AI uses to make recommendations. Not fake reviews — real customers, real words, engineered to trigger AI citations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw__card reveal">
      <div class="hiw__card-video">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
          <source src="/assets/geo/what-we-do/schema-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw__card-body">
        <div class="hiw__step">STEP 03</div>
        <h3 class="hiw__card-title" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s3title">Schema & Content Optimization</h3>
        <p class="hiw__card-text" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s3text">We deploy structured data, llms.txt, and GEO-optimized content that AI crawlers actually understand. Your website becomes machine-readable, not just human-readable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw__card reveal">
      <div class="hiw__card-video">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
          <source src="/assets/geo/what-we-do/monitoring-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw__card-body">
        <div class="hiw__step">STEP 04</div>
        <h3 class="hiw__card-title" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s4title">Weekly AI Monitoring</h3>
        <p class="hiw__card-text" data-i18n="geo.hiw.s4text">Every week we track what AI says about you across all platforms. When algorithms shift, we adapt your strategy the same week. You get a report, action items, and results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hiw {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .container { max-width: var(--container-max); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .hiw__header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12); }
  .hiw__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .hiw__sub {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .hiw__scroll {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    padding: 0 max(20px, calc((100vw - var(--container-max)) / 2 + 20px));
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .hiw__scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

  .hiw__card {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 360px;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-surface-4);
    transition: transform var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-spring),
                box-shadow var(--duration-slow);
  }
  .hiw__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .hiw__card-video {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-surface-4);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .hiw__card-video video {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hiw__card-body { padding: 28px 24px 32px; }
  .hiw__step {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .hiw__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .hiw__card-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hiw__card { width: 300px; }
  }
</style>
